  "text": "Quantification of myofibroblasts was performed using sections immunolabelled with mouse monoclonal antibody to α-smooth muscle actin (#0851; DAKO, Carpinteria, CA; 1:100) plus anti-mouse EnVision System (#4001; DAKO; 1:20) as previously described [CITATION_1] . Volume density of myofibroblasts was evaluated using point counting, x40 objective lens and videomicroscopic system as previously described [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . The results were presented as volume density of myofibroblasts (Vv [myofibroblasts] %).",
